data.description: One-of-a-kind home on a secluded lot in Plattsmouth! The home features 4 bedrooms and several living areas. This huge 2 story with lots of room to spread out has nice siding on most of house with a little bit of it needing to be finished/repaired. There has been lots of upgrades to kitchen and bathroom near finished, just needs a little TLC to finish up those upgrades as well. Large attached/detached 2 car garage. House sold AS-IS with no repairs to seller. All measurement approximate.
